data.description: This beautiful 2-story home offers 4357 sq ft of living space, 24 seller owned solar panels, formal living area, office & large family room/kitchen combo area great for entertaining all your guests. The backyard boasts a covered patio & covered BBQ area with a 20 ft countertop with 8 seats, a rock wall with inviting foliage, you are sure to feel at peace in this area and/or be able to entertain comfortably for all of those special occasions.  Let the kitchen bring out the chef in you with the custom gas range & hood, two refrigerators, two dishwashers, two laundry rooms, fine finishes, stainless appliances, huge pantry, center island that was made from one huge granite slab, butler area with wine refrigerator, dramatic decorative tiles and so many other wonderful features. The upstairs has a huge lounge where you could make it into a gaming area, a movie area or whatever you need it to be. Retreat to the private master bedroom with walk in closet & ensuite master bath for relaxing well into the evening. EV is already done. This community offers so much for your growing family & interest. Room for RV or boat storage offered as well as several fruit trees on the property. VA ASSUMABLE @2.25%. THERE ARE WAYS TO ASSUME A VA EVEN IF YOU'RE NOT A VETERAN. ASK YOUR LENDER FOR MORE INFO.
